  <DialogueData>k__BackingField:
    <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Pax
    <CharacterPortrait>k__BackingField: {fileID: -1162642704207133085, guid: 10a8e30b7d8b77943ae72d49ed6c1f9b, type: 3}
    <DialogueLines>k__BackingField:
    - Now a minigame has appeared too!
    - It is a short task which, once completed, gives you some money.
    - The downside is that you can't attend to the emergencies while playing it,
      so use it with care.
    - You can use the reward money to keep moving units around.
    - If you win, you will keep all the money you were left with. If you don't you
      will receive a smaller sum.
    - This is all you need to know. Don't forget to also check the upgrades in the
      HUB at the end of the round.
    - Good luck!
